Touch Screen
============

|product| is equipped with a multi-point capacitive touch screen. Its multitouch detection capability enables implementation of some advanced GUI operations,
such as two-finger zoom or rotation. 

The capacitive touch screen can be operated by fingers, gloves with a special coating, or a conductive stylus.

.. container:: hatnote hatnote-yellow

  **Size/Type:** |dispsize| multi-point capacitive touch screen |br|
  **Touch screen structure:** G+F+F |br|
  **Surface Strength:** 7H |br|
  **Surface Hardness:** 50G steel ball 70cm impact drop 3 times not broken |br|
  **Service Life (MTBF):** 50 million touch events |br|
  **Light Transmittance:** > 92% |br|
  
:pagebreak:`True`
